00:06.800 --> 00:08.631
Earth to earth,

00:08.670 --> 00:09.364
ashes to ashes,

00:09.410 --> 00:11.605
dust to dust.

00:11.640 --> 00:14.507
The Lord bless him and keep him,

00:14.540 --> 00:19.375
the Lord lift up his countenance
upon him, and give him...

00:19.420 --> 00:21.149
If the Lord had
any sense at all,

00:21.180 --> 00:22.545
he would kick Warren Pendry
right up his ass

00:22.590 --> 00:25.548
and send him to a very
warm place indeed.

00:25.590 --> 00:27.251
(mourners murmuring)
This is a private ceremony.

00:27.290 --> 00:28.712
MAN:
Leave now.

00:28.760 --> 00:29.727
There's an injunction
against you.

00:29.760 --> 00:31.182
You can't be here.

00:31.230 --> 00:33.198
Not until I've paid
my respects, Lawrence.

00:33.230 --> 00:34.219
So you prefer to be arrested?

00:34.260 --> 00:36.069
No, no, I'd prefer,

00:36.100 --> 00:38.694
if you don't mind,

00:38.730 --> 00:40.334
to finish my business!

00:40.370 --> 00:41.394
(mourners exclaiming)
No, no, no, no,

00:41.440 --> 00:42.634
ladies and gentlemen, please.

00:42.670 --> 00:44.331
Don't go!
Don't run away!

00:44.370 --> 00:46.474
I'm an officer of the law!

00:46.510 --> 00:49.741
Or at least I was
an officer of the law,

00:49.780 --> 00:51.338
