clearly departed father

00:51.380 --> 00:54.315
set an army of
solicitors upon me,

00:54.350 --> 00:56.215
and they did a dance
on my reputation, did they not?

00:56.250 --> 00:57.547
You ruined your own career.

00:57.590 --> 00:59.285
This man,
ladies and gentlemen,

00:59.320 --> 01:01.288
this man standing before you,

01:01.320 --> 01:03.481
