for trying to bloody prove it!

01:11.700 --> 01:13.668
My case against you,
Lawrence,

01:13.700 --> 01:15.497
might be in tatters,

01:15.540 --> 01:19.306
but that doesn't mean that
he gets to go In the ground

01:19.340 --> 01:20.432
without somebody standing up

01:20.480 --> 01:22.801
