he truly, truly was.

01:27.320 --> 01:29.379
Hello, Warren.

01:30.890 --> 01:33.586
It's me.

01:33.620 --> 01:35.281
Lestrade.

01:35.320 --> 01:36.787
You thought you took
the you-know-what

01:36.830 --> 01:39.128
out of me, didn't you?

01:39.160 --> 01:41.526
You were wrong.

01:56.450 --> 01:58.702
(cooing)

02:00.580 --> 02:02.241
(sighs)

02:02.290 --> 02:03.518
You're supposed
to be at a meeting.

02:03.550 --> 02:06.257
You receive my text?

02:06.290 --> 02:07.712
"In pursuit of pigeons.

02:07.760 --> 02:10.581
Need you Washington
Square Park ASAP."

02:10.630 --> 02:12.848
What does that
mean, exactly?

02:12.900 --> 02:14.720
As I sat in that
church basement,

02:14.760 --> 02:16.523
the droning of
my fellow addicts

02:16.570 --> 02:17.764
had a powerful
hypnotic effect.

02:17.800 --> 02:19.233
I had a breakthrough.

02:19.270 --> 02:20.567
The problem at hand:

02:20.600 --> 02:21.760
three US. Attorneys

02:21.800 --> 02:23.506
have been murdered
In the last year,

02:23.540 --> 02:24.564
all of them involved
In the prosecutIon

02:24.610 --> 02:26.339
of a syndicate of pirates.

02:26.380 --> 02:28.439
Yes, I know.
I'm working on
the case, too.

02:28.480 --> 02:29.742
Well, precision
in all things, Watson.

02:29.780 --> 02:31.407
When one is constructing
a geometric proof,

02:31.450 --> 02:33.941
