02:39.560 --> 02:40.515
But we have no evidence

02:40.560 --> 02:42.687
linking him to the crimes
or the Syndicate.

02:42.730 --> 02:44.550
We have no idea _
how they are communIcatIng.

02:44.590 --> 02:47.696
Had no idea, I should say.

02:47.730 --> 02:48.924
What, you figured it out?

02:48.960 --> 02:50.621
They use carrier pigeons.

02:50.670 --> 02:51.694
(cooing)

02:51.730 --> 02:53.368
Carrier pigeons.

02:53.400 --> 02:54.765
I staked out
Tomsa's apartment,

02:54.800 --> 02:56.859
Lo and behold,
he had a visit from a bird

02:56.910 --> 02:58.559
