to read the message.

03:09.590 --> 03:11.740
We'll have our connection.

03:36.750 --> 03:38.672
Hey, watch it!

03:49.430 --> 03:51.421
(indistinct conversations)

03:54.300 --> 03:55.756
(grunting)

03:59.770 --> 04:01.738
