to your self-defense.

04:01.770 --> 04:03.260
Well done.

04:03.310 --> 04:05.699
(man wheezing)

04:07.510 --> 04:09.671
(indistinct radio communication)

04:11.610 --> 04:13.669
Department's got
six guys grinding this case,

04:13.720 --> 04:16.348
