Happy hunting.

04:23.730 --> 04:25.322
OFFICER:
Ms. Watson, can I
take a statement?

04:27.530 --> 04:28.792
Sherlock Holmes.

04:30.700 --> 04:33.339
Y-Yes, I'm fine, thank you.

04:34.870 --> 04:36.337
What?

04:39.710 --> 04:40.802
Oh, yes, of course.

04:40.840 --> 04:42.398
