to go to London.

05:29.890 --> 05:31.858
My relationship with Lestrade
started as a marriage

05:31.890 --> 05:33.357
of convenience.

05:33.400 --> 05:34.549
When it came to those
at Scotland Yard

05:34.600 --> 05:37.125
who agreed to work with me,
he was the best

05:37.170 --> 05:38.489
of a bad bunch.

05:38.530 --> 05:39.736
He gave me access
to sensitive cases,

05:39.770 --> 05:40.964
I gave him answers.

05:41.000 --> 05:42.501
_ You never
mentIoned hIm before.

05:42.540 --> 05:44.508
