06:18.610 --> 06:20.430
You feel guilty.

06:20.480 --> 06:21.970
I'm well aware of the corrupting
power of the spotlight.

06:22.010 --> 06:23.602
I avoid it at all costs,

06:23.650 --> 06:25.606
