06:44.700 --> 06:46.019
Well, without you,
the airline might

06:46.070 --> 06:47.867
seat me next to
a morbIdly obese person.

06:47.900 --> 06:49.504
Or a child.

06:49.540 --> 06:52.031
Or a morbidly
obese child.

06:52.070 --> 06:53.628
WATSON: You know, when I first
started working with you,

06:53.680 --> 06:57.172
you mentioned that you
left London in disgrace.

06:57.210 --> 06:59.098
Have you thought about
what it's gonna be like

06:59.150 --> 07:00.640
