DCI Hopkins.

08:10.590 --> 08:11.579
Good to see you.

08:13.060 --> 08:14.550
Good God, man.

08:14.590 --> 08:16.854
You look exactly
the same.
As do you.

08:16.890 --> 08:18.187
Save for the fact
that you've gained

08:18.230 --> 08:19.993
exactly one and
a quarter stone

08:20.030 --> 08:21.657
and your hairline's
receded half a centimeter.

08:21.700 --> 08:23.725
Hey, you're slipping.

08:23.770 --> 08:25.726
I've gained exactly
one and a half stone.

08:25.770 --> 08:27.067
Oh, I'm not slipping;

08:27.100 --> 08:28.636
I've just grown
more courteous.

08:30.270 --> 08:32.738
His name's
Lawrence Pendry.

08:32.780 --> 08:35.101
Son of Warren Pendry.

08:35.140 --> 08:36.277
HOLMES:
British media mogul.

08:36.310 --> 08:37.902
Owns half the papers
in England.

08:37.950 --> 08:39.577
Owned.

08:39.620 --> 08:40.678
Died last week,
heart attack.

08:40.720 --> 08:42.711
But we'll get to that.

08:42.750 --> 08:44.581
13 months ago,
Lawrence here,

08:44.620 --> 08:46.019
