at the scene.

09:17.850 --> 09:20.284
So if Lawrence killed Mary,

09:20.320 --> 09:21.787
then he had
to get rid of the gun

09:21.820 --> 09:23.048
in that eight-minute period.

09:25.060 --> 09:27.654
(boat horn blares)

09:27.700 --> 09:31.591
After you left for the States,
Lestrade struggled.

09:31.630 --> 09:33.837
Cut some corners...

09:33.870 --> 09:35.235
Whatever it took
to close a case.

09:35.270 --> 09:38.865
Warren Pendry
proceeded to use his papers

09:38.910 --> 09:40.878
to paint a very ugly picture,

09:40.910 --> 09:43.242
not just of Lestrade,
but of the Yard in general.

09:43.280 --> 09:45.601
DCS had no choice
but to suspend Lestrade,

09:45.650 --> 09:47.345
pending an investigation.

09:47.380 --> 09:48.779
When was this?

09:48.820 --> 09:49.980
Two weeks ago.
Now, back to Warren...

09:50.020 --> 09:52.750
His funeral was
three days ago.

09:52.790 --> 09:57.750
Lestrade used this
to make an appearance.

09:57.790 --> 10:00.054
It's a fake.
Nevertheless,

10:00.100 --> 10:01.795
it's landed Lestrade

10:01.830 --> 10:03.229
