of trouble.

10:03.270 --> 10:05.625
There's been a manhunt
the last few days,

10:05.670 --> 10:06.637
but it's turned up nothing.

10:06.670 --> 10:07.989
Do you think he did it?

10:08.040 --> 10:10.008
At least two dozen mourners
saw the whole thing.

10:10.040 --> 10:12.167
I'm not talking about Lestrade,
I'm talking about Pendry.

10:12.210 --> 10:13.905
