of his greatest successes.

10:52.850 --> 10:54.772
You give me
too much credit.
I think
you're the one

10:54.820 --> 10:56.913
who gave too much credit.

10:56.950 --> 10:58.383
Please don't misunderstand me,
Holmes, I...

10:58.420 --> 10:59.785
